<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink352">
<l>viḻuttoṭai maṟavar villiṭat tolaintō</l>
<l>reḻuttuṭai naṭuka laṉṉa viḻuppiṇarp</l>
<l>peruṅkai yāṉai yiruñciṉa muṟaikkum</l>
<l>veñcura mariya veṉṉār</l>
<l>vantaṉar tōḻinaṅ kāta lōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Our beloved has returned, my friend, </l>
<l>he who would not call harsh the scorching desert, </l>
<l>where fierce is the great wrath of elephants, their beautiful coarse large trunks, </l>
<l>resembling engraved memorial stones of those who died, </l>
<l>when bold warriors excellent in archery, shot from their bows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
